### Development

```bash
curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh
uv venv --python=3.12 .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
git clone https://github.com/hmartiros/society.git
uv pip install -r requirements.txt
society
```

```
society dev
```
